\f0\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf2 \cb4 Excellent. Since you're interested in a starter script, let's look at 
\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Remotion
