\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf2 \cb4 1. The Composition\cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa200\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf2 \cb4 In Remotion, a 
\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 Composition
\f0\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  is like your canvas. You define the dimensions, duration (in frames), and the frame rate (
\f7\i\fs38\fsmilli19360 \AppleTypeServices FPS
