\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cf2 \cb4 Pro Creator Tips for 2026:\cb1 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa200\partightenfactor0
\ls18\ilvl0\cf2 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	1	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Z-Index Management:
\f0\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  When using PNGs, ensure your "Subject" layer is always higher in Z-index than the "Background" but lower than "Captions."\cb1 \
\ls18\ilvl0
\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	2	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Asset Format:
\f0\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  Use 
\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 WebP
\f0\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539  instead of PNG where possible for your layers; they support transparency and are significantly faster for Remotion to render.\cb1 \
\ls18\ilvl0
\f4\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF65539 \cb4 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	3	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Spring Everything:
